How right were the exit polls?

How accurate were the exit polls this time? On track, but they certainly underestimated just how a wide a net the saffron party would cast in UP and Uttarakhand, while in Punjab, they over-estimated AAP’s impact. In Goa and Manipur it’s been a relatively close call. Here are the details… 
